===Noun===
'''cosine'''

# (''trigonometry'') The ratio of the [[adjacent leg]] to the [[hypotenuse]] of a [[right triangle]] with the given acute angle.
# (''mathematics'') The ''x'' coordinate of the point on the unit circle at the given counterclockwise angle from the ''x'' axis.
# (''mathematics'') The sum of the real or complex [[power series]]
::<math>\sum_0^\infty{{(-1)^{n}}\over{(2n)!}}x^{2n}</math>

